<div id="siteNotice"><!-- CentralNotice --></div>
<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="de"><span dir="auto">Bartgeier</span></h1>
<div id="bodyContent" class="mw-body-content">
<div id="siteSub">aus Wikipedia, der freien Enzyklopädie</div>
<div id="contentSub">(Weitergeleitet von <a href="http://de.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Gypaetus_barbatus&amp;redirect=no" title="Gypaetus barbatus">Gypaetus barbatus</a>)<br />
</div>
<div id="jump-to-nav" class="mw-jump">
